                  {{#if multipleTickets}}tickets{{else}}ticket{{/if}}.
                  We're thrilled to have you join us!
               </p>

               <p class="paragraph">
                  We've created a secure account just for you, where your
                  {{#if multipleTickets}}tickets are{{else}}ticket is{{/if}}
                  safely stored. Simply click the button below to access
                  {{#if multipleTickets}}them{{else}}it{{/if}} and prepare
